Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸被奪走的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓…子…
